---
title: Creamy Garlic Chicken Grain Bowls with Marinated Tomato & Lemon
description: Creamy garlic chicken grain bowls sure sound delicious and hearty, but can they be made in 10 minutes or less? The answer is a resounding yes, thanks to the prowess of your microwave and a few quick prep steps you’ll knock out in no time. That’s right, mealtime can be quick, nourishing, and most importantly, satisfying—a feeling you’re sure to enjoy while you’re drizzling on the homemade tangy garlic sauce that brings this flavorful meal together. Hit it with a squeeze of lemon juice just before serving for a bright, fresh finish.
